## Introduction <a name="intro"></a>

This application allows to evaluate and monitor vegetation dynamic, productivity and land degradation through a *landscape based approach* using *Google EarthEngine* and *LandSat* images.

**This version is a Python translation** of the original GEE JavaScript application. It provides both pure-Python (NumPy) implementations that can be tested and run locally, and GEE server-side modules that mirror the same logic on Earth Engine.
 
